{"tid":1601452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"我地需要東南亞或者中亞","createTime":"2019-09-29T05:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T05:51:06.000Z","uid":165683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"714ca8784a0576e3538755c73717bb42599d15d6","tid":1601452,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://freehk.live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffreehk.live&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2Be0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=97f14a84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://freehk.live</a><br />\n<br />\n東南亞係上世紀反中共運動的支柱<br />\n中亞突厥族同南海各主權被損國家<br />\n根據數據係反共最強的一群<br />\n<br />\n我地可以發起一個主題為反中共極權運動<br />\n針對數據就不同議題發動遊行<br />\n包括殖民西藏,東突厥種族清洗,侵犯南海,侵佔蒙古土地,非法貿易行為,滲透澳洲<br />\n將運動扣連當地利益，將中國受到的壓力最大化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EFbfqf9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEFbfqf9.png&h=20299b1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZVcsuu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZVcsuu.png&h=fb0779f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74e09ad828971494eaddc91f1b7eb4150fabb54f","tid":1601452,"uid":163404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4955b0b050b0f12872449665e5453003c18ffbc","tid":1601452,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:25:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"22e33a31f30389a4f7346cf11ebe0c3b1bd6885a","tid":1601452,"uid":174832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9312a687660245ab7fd8a896d760ffa45a9d1d","tid":1601452,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:40:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"587d615c6ae45a0b3967366114e7294510550609","tid":1601452,"u